    Station Allocation Procedure: Aleutian Islands and Gulf of Alaska Bottom Trawl Surveys

    This package is intended to be used to document and reproduce the station allocation for the Aleutian Islands (even years, 2022-on) and Gulf of Alaska (odd years, 2025-on) bottom trawl surveys. This package is intended to formalize the set of functions saved on the G drive (G:/GOA/R/survey planning/.RData).

    Install 

    library(devtools)
devtools::install_github("barcaroli/SamplingStrata")
devtools::install_github("afsc-gap-products/StationAllocationAIGOA")
